Hi,
This patch updates include/asm-m32r/system.h.
Please apply.
	* include/asm-m32r/system.h:
	- Use barrier() as mb().
	- Change __inline__ to inline.
Thanks,
Signed-off-by: Hirokazu Takata <takata@linux-m32r.org>
